<refentry id='testvoms1'>
<refmeta>
<refentrytitle>testvoms</refentrytitle>
<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>
<refmiscinfo class='source'>VOMS Test Suite</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv id='name'>
<refname>testvoms</refname>
<refpurpose>runs the VOMS test suite</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv id='synopsis'>
<cmdsynopsis>
<command>testvoms</command>
<group choice='opt'>
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>mysql</replaceable></arg>
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>voms</replaceable></arg>
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>voms-proxy-init</replaceable></arg>
</group>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1 id='description'><title>Description</title>
<para>The testvoms command runs the VOMS test suite. It consists of three sets of test:
MySQL configuration tests, VOMS configuration tests and voms-proxy-init configuration tests.</para>

<para>By default the three groups are executed in sequence, but it is possible to execute only a
specific group of tests by specifying its name on the command line.</para>

</refsect1>

